25|$|The {{price of}} an MBS pool is also {{influenced}} by the loan balance. Common specifications for MBS pools are loan amount ranges that each mortgage in the pool must pass. Typically, high-premium (high-coupon) MBSs backed by mortgages with an <b>original</b> <b>loan</b> <b>balance</b> no larger than $85,000 command the largest pay-ups. Even though the borrower is paying an above market yield, {{he or she is}} dissuaded from refinancing a small loan balance due to the high fixed cost involved.|$|E
